        <briefdescription>
<para>XV_hcresampler_ConfigTable. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This table contains configuration structures for the <ref refid="struct_x_v__hcresampler" kindref="compound">XV_hcresampler</ref> driver. Each entry represents the configuration parameters for a specific instance of the v-hcresampler hardware core.</para><para>Fields:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>compatible: Hardware core compatibility string.</para></listitem><listitem><para>reg: Base address of the hardware core.</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,samples-per-clock: Number of samples processed per clock cycle.</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,max-cols: Maximum number of columns supported.</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,max-rows: Maximum number of rows supported.</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,max-data-width: Maximum data width supported.</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,convert-type: Type of conversion performed by the core.</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,num-h-taps: Number of horizontal filter taps.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><para>The final entry with NULL indicates the end of the configuration table. </para>        </detaileddescription>
